{"tid":2193384,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入法出–免疫治療(Immunotherapy)手段醫治癌症(3)","createTime":"2020-09-07T20:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T21:19:33.000Z","uid":38861,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb6a2367c2f29c1da04a37537d2cefb0d0d7182","tid":2193384,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:41:43.000Z","msg":"這系列的第一集，我們講解了PD1/PDL1的運作原理。<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/471125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F471125&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=630cda42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/471125</a><br />\n<br />\n第二集我們講述了CTLA4與T cell功用的關係。<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/472480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F472480&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=7b689939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/472480</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cu3nRnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcu3nRnn.jpg&h=8fed36bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次第三集這一篇，我們將會講述增加T cell有效抵達癌細胞所在位置的其中一種手段。<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)有不少種類的癌細胞會抑壓與免疫系統相關的機制（RIG-1，JAK，PKR等等），從而盡量減低T cell或免疫細胞前來自身位置的機會。<br />\n<br />\n但免疫系統機制的喪失或銳弱，換來的將會是失去抵禦病毒入侵的能力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZpuwnt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZpuwnt.jpg&h=21438d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而能夠在癌細胞裡頭任意進行複製及破壞的病毒，又不會對普通細胞進行過大傷害的，我們稱它為Oncolytic virus。<br />\n<br />\n這些Oncolytic virus可以是自然存在的病毒，亦可以是被基因改造過的人工病毒。<br />\n2006年，中國批准利用Oncolytic virus手段醫治鼻咽癌，而2015年美國FDA及歐洲EMA亦批准這種手段可以用在醫治皮膚癌之上。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）近日有科學家發表文章（Ref1)，結合Oncolytic virus及免疫系統治療方式來醫治實驗室細胞及老鼠身上的癌細胞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XgwD89b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgwD89b.jpg&h=6f57ace0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他們利用基因改造方式製作Oncolytic virus，目的就是想細胞被病毒感染後會不斷產生沒有功用的tCD19組件。<br />\n<br />\n在圖中可以清楚看得見，標記為藍色的癌細胞受到病毒感染後，會在自己外圍生產被標記為粉紅色的tCD19組件。<br />\n<br />\n其後，他們製作出能夠辨認tCD19的T cell（整套技術的學術名稱為Chimeric antigen receptor T cell，這裡我們稱之為tCD19-CAR T cell)，再放入老鼠身體之內。<br />\n<br />\n這些tCD19-CAR T cell只會辨認外圍擁有tCD19的細胞，並對其進行殲滅。<br />\n<br />\n因為tCD19並不自然存在普通細胞裡，所以它們只會殺滅受病毒感染的癌細胞；<br />\n普通健康細胞擁有健全的免疫系統相關機制，因此能夠阻止病毒在自己裡頭繁殖，亦避免了tCD19的產生。<br />\n<br />\n他們在文章清楚顯示，加進Oncolytic virus及tCD19-CAR T cell後能夠有效殺滅老鼠身上的癌細胞。同時他們亦發現得到，癌細胞被殺滅後會同時釋發出病毒，而病毒亦會順之然感染附近的癌細胞，以火燒連環船的方式將tCD19散發開去。<br />\n<br />\n這種手段能否在人體上實際運用，還需要一系列的改進及臨床實驗才能得出結論，但無疑的是若然能夠成功配上Oncolytic Virus及CAR Tcell的組合，定必能夠加強免疫細胞鎖定癌細胞所在位置的能力，以三管齊下的方式（PD1/CLTA4/Virus-CARTCell）把癌細胞滅絕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLWs2ug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLWs2ug.jpg&h=9253d200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=ea67b41a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=ae63f563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://stm.sciencemag.org/content/12/559/eaaz1863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstm.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F12%2F559%2Feaaz1863&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=239dcf9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stm.sciencemag.org/content/12/559/eaaz1863</a>"},{"pid":"96745b2b7ca26aaffad75c4ecda1c66693b6e45d","tid":2193384,"uid":155238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:49:28.000Z","msg":"薯仔好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d4833f82e30c98f1adb71a3915e38a05167df3","tid":2193384,"uid":358248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:50:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0af8af92c2381502ad73019161c7e73025162e00","tid":2193384,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1d4833f82e30c98f1adb71a3915e38a05167df3","tid":2193384,"uid":358248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:50:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全睇漏眼，fuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8ba5c3faa31b477f3d104a7563cb9c9cde11c1","tid":2193384,"uid":155238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0af8af92c2381502ad73019161c7e73025162e00","tid":2193384,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1d4833f82e30c98f1adb71a3915e38a05167df3","tid":2193384,"uid":358248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:50:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:52:02.000Z","msg"